title: Elvis Presley - The Final Curtain DVD 1
description:

Elvis Presley
The Final Curtain Box Set - DVD 1 of 6
'SUPER 8 MAGIC OF 1977 VOL. 1.'
Dual-Layer DVD9


Still the definitive set of The King in 1977! The set consists of 6 DVDs. Disc 1 & 2 are Dual-Layer and offer first-generation Super 8 footage from '77. Discs 3-5 are single-layer and feature the very best copies of the coveted CBS Tapes. Finally, disc 6 is another Dual-Layer; this time with an anthology of news footage surrounding the death of Elvis.

Please help seed!! I have every intention of uploading all 6 DVDs....but it will take some time.
